description: Modifies the specified project name, given the project ARN and a new name.

parameters.name: arn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the project whose name to update.

parameters.name: vpcConfig
parameters.description: The VPC security groups and subnets that are attached to a project. An array of one or more security groups IDs in your Amazon VPC. (string) --- An array of one or more subnet IDs in your Amazon VPC. (string) --- The ID of the Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: securityGroupIds
nested_params.description: An array of one or more security groups IDs in your Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: subnetIds
nested_params.description: An array of one or more subnet IDs in your Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: vpcId
nested_params.description: The ID of the Amazon VPC.

nested_items.name: defaultJobTimeoutMinutes
nested_items.description: The default number of minutes (at the project level) a test run executes before it times out. The default value is 150 minutes.
